{"title":"🚀PowerShell自用","uid":"9825ba2a9702cab3ab59ca74edda72a8","slug":"tool/PowerShell自用","date":"2020-01-17T15:34:36.000Z","updated":"2024-05-09T15:55:21.985Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/tool/PowerShell自用.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"Install-PowerShell-Preview\"><a href=\"#Install-PowerShell-Preview\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install PowerShell Preview\"></a>Install PowerShell Preview</h2><p>Windows 用户我个人推荐使用 choco 安装 <a href=\"https://chocolatey.org/packages/powershell-preview\">PowerShell Preview</a>，方便快捷，需要使用管理员权限执行安装命令。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装-oh-my-posh\"><a href=\"#安装-oh-my-posh\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 oh-my-posh\"></a>安装 oh-my-posh</h2><p>给 PowerShell 权限去执行任意脚本</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Set-ExecutionPolicy</span> Bypass</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装 <code>posh-git</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Install-Module</span> posh<span class=\"literal\">-git</span> <span class=\"literal\">-Scope</span> CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装 <code>oh-my-posh</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Install-Module</span> <span class=\"built_in\">oh</span><span class=\"literal\">-my-posh</span> <span class=\"literal\">-Scope</span> CurrentUser</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"写入到配置文件\"><a href=\"#写入到配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"写入到配置文件\"></a>写入到配置文件</h2><p>先获取文件路径<br><img src=\"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/powershell%E8%87%AA%E7%94%A8/1.png\"></p>\n<p>这个文件不存在的话就新建一个，写入以下内容：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight powershell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Import-Module</span> posh<span class=\"literal\">-git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Import-Module</span> <span class=\"built_in\">oh</span><span class=\"literal\">-my-posh</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">Set-Theme</span> Sorin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","text":"Install PowerShell PreviewWindows 用户我个人推荐使用 choco 安装 PowerShell Preview，方便快捷，需要使...","permalink":"/post/tool/PowerShell自用","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":377,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Tool","slug":"Tool","count":3,"path":"api/categories/Tool.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"PowerShell","slug":"PowerShell","count":1,"path":"api/tags/PowerShell.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Install-PowerShell-Preview\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Install PowerShell Preview</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-oh-my-posh\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装 oh-my-posh</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%86%99%E5%85%A5%E5%88%B0%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\"><span class=\"toc-text\">写入到配置文件</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"大鹏","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/avator/567.png","link":"/","description":"Web Developer","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/KongValley","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"https://blog-chara-img.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/blog-img/bilibili.svg","link":"https://live.bilib